            | These gases are known as Greenhouse
            | gases. Carbon dioxide, Ozone, Methane,
            | Water Vapour etc. are examples for
            | greenhouse gases. Even though they
            | occur naturally an increase in their
            | amount in the atmosphere cause the
            | phenomenon known as Global Warming.
